let signupForm = {
    Brand_Name_DBA: "Texte",
    Online_Store_Website: "",
    Business_Owner_Email: "",
    Federal_Tax_Classification: "",
    Tax_Identification_Number: "",
    Legal_Name_Company: "",
    Street_Number_Steet_Name: "",
    Company_Postal_Code: "",
    Company_City: "",
    Company_Country: "",
    Province_Incorporation: "",
    First_Name: "",
    Last_Name: "",
    Date_Birth: "",
    Residential_Address: "",
    Manager_Postal_Code: "",
    Manager_City: "",
    Manager_Country: "",
    Currency: "",
    Bank_Country: "",
    Account_Holder_Name: "",
    Routing_Number: "",
    Account_Number: ""
};

const signupReducer = (state = signupForm, action) => {
    return state[action.type] = action.payload;
}

export default signupReducer;
